{"title":"CSS水平居中样式的8种实现方式","uid":"0ef5e478d063e387bdfd27538e830494","slug":"css-horizontal-center-in-eight-ways","date":"2025-07-17T10:31:03.000Z","updated":"2025-08-06T12:09:26.524Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/css-horizontal-center-in-eight-ways.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ProselyteCoding/online-assets/main/blog/cover-css.png","content":"<h1 id=\"CSS-水平居中样式的8种实现方式\"><a href=\"#CSS-水平居中样式的8种实现方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS 水平居中样式的8种实现方式\"></a>CSS 水平居中样式的8种实现方式</h1><p>假设需要设置水平居中样式的对象是 <code>item</code> ，其父元素为 <code>container</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-text-align-center\"><a href=\"#1-text-align-center\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. text-align: center\"></a>1. text-align: center</h2><p>行内元素水平居中(在父元素上设定)<br><em>只对行内元素(inline、inline-block)有效</em></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">text-align</span>: center;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-margin-0-auto\"><a href=\"#2-margin-0-auto\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. margin: 0 auto\"></a>2. margin: 0 auto</h2><p>块级元素水平居中<br><em>需要指定宽度，只对块级元素有效</em></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.item</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"number\">200px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"3-flex-justify-content\"><a href=\"#3-flex-justify-content\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. flex + justify-content\"></a>3. flex + justify-content</h2><p>Flexbox 水平居中<br><em>在 flex 容器上设置，适用于所有子元素</em></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">justify-content</span>: center;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"4-flex-margin-auto\"><a href=\"#4-flex-margin-auto\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. flex + margin auto\"></a>4. flex + margin auto</h2><p>Flexbox 中单个项目水平居中<br><em>在 flex 项目上设置，配合 <code>display: flex</code> 使用</em></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: flex;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.item</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">margin</span>: <span class=\"number\">0</span> auto;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"5-grid-justify-items\"><a href=\"#5-grid-justify-items\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. grid + justify-items\"></a>5. grid + justify-items</h2><p>Grid 水平居中所有项目</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: grid;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">justify-items</span>: center;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"6-grid-justify-self\"><a href=\"#6-grid-justify-self\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. grid + justify-self\"></a>6. grid + justify-self</h2><p>Grid 水平居中单个项目</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: grid;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.item</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">justify-self</span>: center;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"7-absolute-transform\"><a href=\"#7-absolute-transform\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7. absolute + transform\"></a>7. absolute + transform</h2><p>绝对定位水平居中<br><em>需要设置父元素为相对定位，即 <code>position: relative</code></em></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">position</span>: absolute;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">left</span>: <span class=\"number\">50%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">translateX</span>(-<span class=\"number\">50%</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"8-absolute-负-margin\"><a href=\"#8-absolute-负-margin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8. absolute + 负 margin\"></a>8. absolute + 负 margin</h2><p>绝对定位水平居中(已知宽度)<br><em>需要知道元素确切宽度</em></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">position</span>: absolute;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">left</span>: <span class=\"number\">50%</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"number\">200px</span>; <span class=\"comment\">/* 确定宽度 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">margin-left</span>: -<span class=\"number\">100px</span>; <span class=\"comment\">/* 宽度的一半 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n","text":"CSS 水平居中样式的8种实现方式假设需要设置水平居中样式的对象是 item ，其父元素为 container 1. text-align: center行内元...","permalink":"/post/css-horizontal-center-in-eight-ways","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端